snippet.title: Crowman & Wolfboy - Opening Scene
snippet.description:
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/crowman-wolfboy/id703247992?mt=8

Crowman & Wolfboy is an action/adventure game, now available on iOS devices. Save shadow babies! Collect light orbs! Fend off an ancient evil as you help Crowman & Wolfboy escape the Darkness of their home world and seek out the mysterious "humans"!


LIKE Crowman & Wolfboy at: https://www.facebook.com/CandWiOS
